---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Code of Conduct"
  description="The OpenTeams Code of Conduct. Treat everyone with respect. A pledge from everyone in the OpenTeams community to uphold a collaborative, inclusive culture."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="OpenTeams Code of Conduct"
    title="Code of Conduct"
    lead="The essentials: treat everyone with respect. Avoid insults, demeaning remarks, and unprofessional behavior. Remember that we are a global, diverse community."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>
          We firmly believe in the strength and vibrancy that a diverse
          community brings to software development and scientific advancement.
          Diversity not only broadens our potential contributor base and idea
          pool but also challenges our assumptions, driving innovation and
          development.
        </p>

        <h2>Recognizing Specific Identities</h2>
        <p>
          While our diversity statement is universally inclusive, we acknowledge
          the specific challenges faced by identities affected by systemic
          discrimination. OpenTeams invites everyone to engage with our
          community, valuing each unique identity and background.
        </p>

        <h2>Introduction &amp; Scope</h2>
        <p>
          This code of conduct is a pledge from everyone in the OpenTeams
          community and is expected to be upheld in all OpenTeams-related
          activities and by anyone affiliated with OpenTeams. It applies across
          all community spaces, including digital platforms, events, and any
          communication channels, embodying our ideals of a collaborative,
          inclusive culture.
        </p>

        <h2>Standards for Behavior</h2>
        <p>
          OpenTeams is a global nexus of diverse professionals. We advocate for:
        </p>

        <h3>Empathy and Kindness</h3>
        <p>
          Treating each other with understanding and kindness, fostering a
          welcoming environment.
        </p>

        <h3>Collaboration</h3>
        <p>
          Emphasizing teamwork and dependency across projects, valuing friendly,
          effective collaboration.
        </p>

        <h3>Inquisitiveness</h3>
        <p>
          Encouraging questions and continuous learning, fostering an
          environment where curiosity drives progress.
        </p>

        <h3>Respectful Communication</h3>
        <p>
          Choosing our words carefully, respecting all community members, and
          avoiding any form of derogatory comments.
        </p>

        <h2>Unacceptable Behavior</h2>
        <p>
          OpenTeams does not tolerate harassment or exclusionary behavior. This
          includes, but is not limited to, the use of sexualized language or
          imagery, intimidation, discriminatory jokes, and unwelcome sexual
          attention. We are committed to making our community a harassment-free
          zone for everyone.
        </p>

        <h2>Reporting Guidelines</h2>
        <p>
          OpenTeams takes all reports of misconduct seriously to maintain our
          community’s welcoming nature. We encourage timely reporting of any
          behavior that contradicts our code of conduct, ensuring
          confidentiality in all proceedings. Report to{' '}
          <a href="mailto:hr@openteams.com">hr@openteams.com</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Looking Out for Each Other</h2>
        <p>
          We are a community that looks after one another. If you observe a
          situation that might be harmful or against our code of conduct, please
          report it. Together, we can ensure OpenTeams remains a safe, inclusive,
          and vibrant community for all.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose { max-width: 760px; }
  .prose h2 { margin-top: 2.5rem; }
  .prose h3 { margin-top: 1.75rem; }
  .prose h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
</style>
